Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest evidence

Purpose:
  Show source evidence for an object.

Usage:
  spinedigest evidence <archive.sdpub> <id> [--json]

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: yes.

Examples:
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub node:84
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub sentence:1:0:2
